lt go to all that I shall send thee, and whatsoever I command thee thou shalt speak.","year":-629},{"id":"recgBh6Dbkc5HaPlK","ref":"Jer.1.8","text":"Be not afraid of their faces: for I am with thee to deliver thee, saith the LORD.","year":-629}]}
